question: Which of the following medical college of Uttar Pradesh ranked 5th in the list of NIRF Medical College Ranking 2020?
option1: Sanjay Gandhi Postgraduate Institute of Medical Sciences, Lucknow
option3: Banaras Hindu University, Varanasi, Uttar Pradesh
answer: Sanjay Gandhi Postgraduate Institute of Medical Sciences, Lucknow
explanation: Sanjay Gandhi Postgraduate Institute of Medical Sciences, Lucknow ranked 5th in the list of NIRF Medical College Ranking 2020. Banaras Hindu University, Varanasi ranked sixth in the list. All India Institute of Medical Sciences, New Delhi ranked first in the list.
